      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014this car is a total showstopper! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and is in truly flawless condition; it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no stories, just a smooth, beautiful ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure. If you\u2019ve been looking for a gem that\u2019s been treated with nothing but love, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
