      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M\u2019s naturally aspirated heritage. At its heart lies the S65 4.0L V8, a high-revving masterpiece featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional power delivery and corner-exit traction. The vehicle is mechanically flawless, having undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The chassis exhibits zero fatigue, and the factory suspension geometry remains perfectly aligned. Finished in a stunning, swirl-free paint with a cabin that remains in showroom state, this is a turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Pristine interior. Full service records included.",
      "price": 43500.0,
