      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the deep, mirror-like finish of its original factory paint. Inside, the cabin remains in flawless condition; the premium leather upholstery still retains its factory-fresh scent, with absolutely no signs of wear on the bolsters, carpets, or touchpoints. Every electronic feature functions perfectly, and the engine bay is remarkably clean. Mechanically, the car is turn-key, having received preventative maintenance strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a comprehensive folder of service records included. With zero door dings, no curb rash on the wheels, and a spotless undercarriage, this is as close to a new vehicle as you can find on the pre-owned market. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved masterpiece.",
      "price": 48500.0,
